General.Name: My Rewards International Ltd
General.Description: My Rewards International Limited provides employee benefit, rewards and recognition, employee engagement, loyalty program, and membership services to corporate and retail clients. It serves employees, members, customers, and businesses. The company was formerly known as The Rewards Factory Limited and changed its name to My Rewards International Limited in May 2011. My Rewards International Limited was incorporated in 2000 and is based in St Kilda, Australia.
